entries.femaleVariant: Vega's takin' a little nap in the trunk, no civs hit – yeah, knew you were the right one for the job.

Do the words "for the public good" mean anything to you, V? 'Cause what you pulled back there – that shit was the opposite of good.
Hey, I already sent the car. You were just supposed to knock Vega out, toss him in the trunk.
I know the scopsucker deserved to die, but… well, at least there wasn't any collateral damage.
Community's suffered enough as it is. Gig closed.
Vega's flatlined and no one else is, so I'll chalk that up as a "win."
Those people have suffered enough. Christ… But at least Vega's fuckin' dead. Gig closed.
What the hell happened? I already sent the car!
Although the end can justify the means, sometimes. Let's hope that's the case here.
Contract closed, but for future reference – a light touch can still get the job done.

Nice work, V. All Night City thanks you. Gig closed and sealed.
